{"tid":1436343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登愛國  福音戒獨  #福獨","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T18:56:23.000Z","uid":281874,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"51eaa3448704f4e02e95ca9bcc61117c0ee783f5","tid":1436343,"uid":281874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"經過呢場運動，相信就算唔係教徒嘅同路人，都唱到兩句&ldquo;sing hallelujah to the lord&quot;<br />\n雖然呢個月福音絕跡，但係面對嚟緊嘅進擊之福建人，我誠意推介愛國愛港嘅連登巴絲，「福音戒獨」計劃  （以下簡稱「福獨」）<br />\n<br />\n首先梗係要講<strong><ins>背景</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHWzzcy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHWzzcy.png&h=d846a1e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n勇武嘅福建人，領先全國，勁過帝吧，出征香港痛擊港獨勢力，實在係我共之福；我諗全國14億人，包括福建人，成世人無諗過自己咁威，愛國愛港嘅香港人一定要吹捧福建人，成為全國第一大族。<br />\n<br />\n然後講下<strong><ins>近況</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cUZpWr6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcUZpWr6.jpg&h=5ff6564e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7xDmYFr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7xDmYFr.jpg&h=d58be317&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n根據未FC，但都似層層嘅圖片顯示，福建大軍已經早過解放軍，陸續君臨香港，不過睇相佢哋好似唔多識路；作為愛國愛港嘅香港人，梗係要迎接佢哋，俾全世界見到福建人嘅低調。<br />\n<br />\n仲有多個<strong><ins>未FC資訊</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B3V8DGi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB3V8DGi.png&h=91ae294a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提議一： #福獨<br />\n<strong>福音戒獨    Fxxking Independent    福獨   </strong> 字樣嘅banner，如果由詠唱&ldquo;sing hallelujah to the lord&quot;嘅愛國愛港人仕手持，與福建幫同行，支持佢哋，相信會令福建人賓至如歸，甚至有興趣影相俾朋友 ／ 帶啲banner過境返鄉下威威添  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n提議一： 福建人牛B<br />\n<strong> 福建人牛B    支持福建人</strong>    等等嘅字眼，如果用筆大大隻寫上舊衫 （唔好印啦，環保啲），然後著出去恭迎福建幫，相信佢哋望住你，點都打唔落手，可能仲會攬住你影張相添。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇個勢，福建幫周末就會到，大家一齊好唔認真咁認真啲諗計仔，<del>迎戰</del>  迎接佢哋；一來要減低傷亡，二來可以向全國散播 #福獨 種子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b8PmehY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb8PmehY.png&h=25cd4c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n廣州人民都開始覺醒，自發學習更多真相同方式；難得福建幫肉體翻牆，千里迢迢來港，過門都係客，我哋一定要準備充足！"},{"pid":"615bf0e28d95457e305763f5f025effe1a8fe816","tid":1436343,"uid":281874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:38:27.000Z","msg":"反港獨   撐福獨<br />\n<br />\n拉埋啦啦球去酒店門口，迎接福建人嚟香港<br />\n<br />\n歡迎福建  支持福建"},{"pid":"68d8033e77e9edced79eb5e1f32219ab77775773","tid":1436343,"uid":258570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:49:01.000Z","msg":"幫推！讓福獨改變世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0e42a4dd59d8d1c213eddafd804fab3c8470fc","tid":1436343,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:56:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港警察</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">知法犯法</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">下流賤格</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一味靠嚇</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">污糟邋遢</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">淪為垃圾</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">吞槍自殺</span></div></span></blockquote>"}]}